Located in Agra, a 20-minute walk from Taj Mahal, Bedweiser Backpackers Hostel has accommodations with a restaurant, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Among the facilities at this property are an ATM and a tour desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides evening entertainment and a 24-hour front desk.

At the hostel, the rooms have a private bathroom with a shower.

A continental breakfast is available each morning at Bedweiser Backpackers Hostel.

Agra Fort is 4 miles from the accommodation, while Jama Masjid is 4.3 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Agra Airport, 7 miles from Bedweiser Backpackers Hostel.

This is our guests' favorite part of Agra, according to independent reviews.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 8.9 for a two-person trip.
